, watching them spring to life. We nail new options to walls on a regular basis. We bake options-cakes and hand them out at parties. Options are good. Options are awesome. We have lots of them. Spend some quality time getting to know your new garden of options in E17. It may just finally give you the control you have been pining for.\"<p><div class=\"share_submission\" style=\"position:relative;\"> <a class=\"slashpop\" href=\"http://twitter.com/home?status=After+12+years+of+Development%2C+E17+Is+Out%3A+http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2FTcUs2C\"><img src=\"http://a.fsdn.com/sd/twitter_icon_large.png\"></a> <a class=\"slashpop\" href=\"http://www.facebook.com/sharer.php?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftech.slashdot.org%2Fstory%2F12%2F12%2F22%2F0129200%2Fafter-12-years-of-development-e17-is-out%3Futm_source%3Dslashdot%26utm_medium%3Dfacebook\"><img src=\"http://a.fsdn.com/sd/facebook_icon_large.png\"></a> <a class=\"nobg\" href=\"http://plus.google.com/share?url=http://tech.slashdot.org/story/12/12/22/0129200/after-12-years-of-development-e17-is-out?utm_source=slashdot&amp;utm_medium=googleplus\" onclick=\"javascript:window.open(this.href,'', 'menubar=no,toolbar=no,resizable=yes,scrollbars=yes,height=600,width=600');return false;\"><img src=\"http://www.gstatic.com/images/icons/gplus-16.png\" alt=\"Share on Google+\"/></a> </div></p><p><a href=\"http://tech.slashdot.org/story/12/12/22/0129200/after-12-years-of-development-e17-is-out?utm_source=rss1.0moreanon&amp;utm_medium=feed\">Read more of this story</a> at Slashdot.</p><iframe src=\"http://slashdot.org/slashdot-it.pl?op=discuss&amp;id=3333697&amp;smallembed=1\" style=\"height: 300px; width: 100%; border: none;\"></iframe><img width='1' height='1' src='http://slashdot.feedsportal.com/c/35028/f/647410/s/26d90663/mf.gif' border='0'/><br/><br/><a href=\"http://da.feedsportal.com/r/151883673614/u/49/f/647410/c/35028/s/26d90663/a2.htm\"><img src=\"http://da.feedsportal.com/r/151883673614/u/49/f/647410/c/35028/s/26d90663/a2.img\" border=\"0\"/></a><