al applications is not merely less perfect than the simple examples seen in school &mdash; it's outright terrible by any number of measures.\"<p><div class=\"share_submission\" style=\"position:relative;\"> <a class=\"slashpop\" href=\"http://twitter.com/home?status=Real+World+Code+Sucks%3A+http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2FUdUfMv\"><img src=\"http://a.fsdn.com/sd/twitter_icon_large.png\"></a> <a class=\"slashpop\" href=\"http://www.facebook.com/sharer.php?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftech.slashdot.org%2Fstory%2F12%2F12%2F21%2F220255%2Freal-world-code-sucks%3Futm_source%3Dslashdot%26utm_medium%3Dfacebook\"><img src=\"http://a.fsdn.com/sd/facebook_icon_large.png\"></a> <a class=\"nobg\" href=\"http://plus.google.com/share?url=http://tech.slashdot.org/story/12/12/21/220255/real-world-code-sucks?utm_source=slashdot&amp;utm_medium=googleplus\" onclick=\"javascript:window.open(this.href,'', 'menubar=no,toolbar=no,resizable=yes,scrollbars=yes,height=600,width=600');return false;\"><img src=\"http://www.gstatic.com/images/icons/gplus-16.png\" alt=\"Share on Google+\"/></a> </div></p><p><a href=\"http://tech.slashdot.org/story/12/12/21/220255/real-world-code-sucks?utm_source=rss1.0moreanon&amp;utm_medium=feed\">Read more of this story</a> at Slashdot.</p><iframe src=\"http://slashdot.org/slashdot-it.pl?op=discuss&amp;id=3333463&amp;smallembed=1\" style=\"height: 300px; width: 100%; border: none;\"></iframe><img width='1' height='1' src='http://slashdot.feedsportal.com/c/35028/f/647410/s/26d8003c/mf.gif' border='0'/><br/><br/><a href=\"http://da.feedsportal.com/r/151883659115/u/49/f/647410/c/35028/s/26d8003c/a2.htm\"><img src=\"http://da.feedsportal.com/r/151883659115/u/49/f/647410/c/35028/s/26d8003c/a2.img\" border=\"0\"/></a><img width=\"1\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://pi.feedsportal.com/r/151883659115/u/49/f/647410/c/35028/s/26d8003c/a2t.img\" border=\"0\"/><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/Slashdot/slashdot/~4/JwZvDJvFA8w\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\"/>") (pubDate nil "Fri, 21 Dec 2012 22:15:0